  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Emiliana lives a simple life as a nun in the remote village of Zamak.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >One day, Mariethas soldiers appear in the village's market on a Witch Hunt. There they capture Emiliana's sister, Laura, accusing her of being a Witch.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In order to save her sister, Emiliana exchanges her soul for the power of a Witch. Now, Emiliana must wrestle with her faith as she searches for her sister.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Classic RPG Experience</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fantasy Setting</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Turn-based Combat</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Leveling System</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Quest System</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\"Demon Flame\" System</p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Emiliana lives a simple life as a nun in the remote village of Zamak.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >One day, Mariethas soldiers appear in the village's market on a Witch Hunt. There they capture Emiliana's sister, Laura, accusing her of being a Witch.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In order to save her sister, Emiliana exchanges her soul for the power of a Witch. Now, Emiliana must wrestle with her faith as she searches for her sister.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Classic RPG Experience</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fantasy Setting</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Turn-based Combat</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Leveling System</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Quest System</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\"Demon Flame\" System</p></li></ul>",
